---
description: JSON-RPC routing and ERC-4337 error contracts
globs:
  - "crates/rpc/src/**/*.rs"
  - "crates/types/src/user_operation/**/*.rs"
---

- Wrap jsonrpsee handlers with `utils::safe_call_rpc_handler`.
- Route user operations by EntryPoint address through `EntryPointRouter`.
- Remember v0.8/v0.9 are distinct EntryPoint versions that share the v0.7 ABI.
- Add or update `EthRpcError` to `ErrorObjectOwned` mappings for client-visible errors.
- Gate privileged or state-mutating endpoints; sponsored delegation is disabled by default for a reason.

Full details: `.agents/skills/rpc-errors/`.
